abstract: Baseball Roundup; Houston Astros defeat Los Angeles Angels, 6-3; other MLB scores and news noted.
lead_paragraph: Houston’s Evan Gattis and Carlos Correa each homered in a matchup of A.L. wild-card contenders. Chicago beat Milwaukee, and its N.L. Central rival St. Louis edged Cincinnati.

headline.main: Astros’ Homers Sink Angels; Cubs and Cardinals Win
headline.print_headline: Astros’ Homers Sink Angels; Cubs and the Cardinals Win
